{"title":"Echarts折线图之平滑设置及MarkPoint配置","slug":"Echarts折线图之平滑设置及MarkPoint配置","date":"2021-09-30T03:47:10.000Z","updated":"2021-09-30T03:47:10.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Echarts折线图之平滑设置及MarkPoint配置.json","excerpt":"本文主要通过对echarts的几个属性设置，使echarts的折线图展示效果更好。","covers":["/2021/09/30/echarts-zhe-xian-tu-zhi-ping-hua-she-zhi-ji-markpoint-pei-zhi/220754231.png"],"content":"<p>本文主要通过对echarts的几个属性设置，使echarts的折线图展示效果更好。</p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n\n<h2 id=\"环境\"><a href=\"#环境\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"环境\"></a>环境</h2><p>OS: windows server 2008<br>Echarts:5.2</p>\n<h2 id=\"折线平滑设置\"><a href=\"#折线平滑设置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"折线平滑设置\"></a>折线平滑设置</h2><p>设置smooth属性为true，如下:</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">series: [\n    &#123;\n      name: &#39;Lowest&#39;,\n      type: &#39;line&#39;,\n      data: [1, -2, 2, 5, 3, 2, 0],\n      smooth:true\n    &#125;\n]<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"空数据连接\"><a href=\"#空数据连接\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"空数据连接\"></a>空数据连接</h2><p>当数据中有空数据时，折线图可能会断掉，如下:<br><img src=\"/2021/09/30/echarts-zhe-xian-tu-zhi-ping-hua-she-zhi-ji-markpoint-pei-zhi/220754231.png\"><br>将connectNulls设置为true即可：<br><img src=\"/2021/09/30/echarts-zhe-xian-tu-zhi-ping-hua-she-zhi-ji-markpoint-pei-zhi/418628742.png\"></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">series: [\n    &#123;\n      name: &#39;Lowest&#39;,\n      type: &#39;line&#39;,\n      data: [1, -2, 2, 5, 3, 2, 0],\n      smooth:true,\n      connectNulls:true\n    &#125;\n]<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"添加最大、最小值、平均线\"><a href=\"#添加最大、最小值、平均线\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"添加最大、最小值、平均线\"></a>添加最大、最小值、平均线</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">series: [\n    &#123;\n      name: &#39;Highest&#39;,\n      type: &#39;line&#39;,\n      data: [10, 11, null, 11, 12, 12, 9],\n      connectNulls:true,\n      markPoint: &#123;\n        data: [\n          &#123; type: &#39;max&#39;, name: &#39;Max&#39; &#125;,\n          &#123; type: &#39;min&#39;, name: &#39;Min&#39; &#125;\n        ]\n      &#125;,\n      markLine: &#123;\n        data: [&#123; type: &#39;average&#39;, name: &#39;Avg&#39; &#125;]\n      &#125;\n    &#125;,<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"References\"><a href=\"#References\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"References\"></a>References</h2><p><a href=\"https://echarts.apache.org/examples/zh/editor.html?c=line-marker\">1、Echarts折线图示例</a><br><a href=\"https://tiezhuzhuzhu923.lofter.com/post/310ff6d7_1c804cbfb\">2、封面图源</a></p>\n","more":"<h2 id=\"环境\"><a href=\"#环境\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"环境\"></a>环境</h2><p>OS: windows server 2008<br>Echarts:5.2</p>\n<h2 id=\"折线平滑设置\"><a href=\"#折线平滑设置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"折线平滑设置\"></a>折线平滑设置</h2><p>设置smooth属性为true，如下:</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">series: [\n    &#123;\n      name: &#39;Lowest&#39;,\n      type: &#39;line&#39;,\n      data: [1, -2, 2, 5, 3, 2, 0],\n      smooth:true\n    &#125;\n]<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"空数据连接\"><a href=\"#空数据连接\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"空数据连接\"></a>空数据连接</h2><p>当数据中有空数据时，折线图可能会断掉，如下:<br><img src=\"/2021/09/30/echarts-zhe-xian-tu-zhi-ping-hua-she-zhi-ji-markpoint-pei-zhi/220754231.png\"><br>将connectNulls设置为true即可：<br><img src=\"/2021/09/30/echarts-zhe-xian-tu-zhi-ping-hua-she-zhi-ji-markpoint-pei-zhi/418628742.png\"></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">series: [\n    &#123;\n      name: &#39;Lowest&#39;,\n      type: &#39;line&#39;,\n      data: [1, -2, 2, 5, 3, 2, 0],\n      smooth:true,\n      connectNulls:true\n    &#125;\n]<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"添加最大、最小值、平均线\"><a href=\"#添加最大、最小值、平均线\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"添加最大、最小值、平均线\"></a>添加最大、最小值、平均线</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">series: [\n    &#123;\n      name: &#39;Highest&#39;,\n      type: &#39;line&#39;,\n      data: [10, 11, null, 11, 12, 12, 9],\n      connectNulls:true,\n      markPoint: &#123;\n        data: [\n          &#123; type: &#39;max&#39;, name: &#39;Max&#39; &#125;,\n          &#123; type: &#39;min&#39;, name: &#39;Min&#39; &#125;\n        ]\n      &#125;,\n      markLine: &#123;\n        data: [&#123; type: &#39;average&#39;, name: &#39;Avg&#39; &#125;]\n      &#125;\n    &#125;,<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"References\"><a href=\"#References\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"References\"></a>References</h2><p><a href=\"https://echarts.apache.org/examples/zh/editor.html?c=line-marker\">1、Echarts折线图示例</a><br><a href=\"https://tiezhuzhuzhu923.lofter.com/post/310ff6d7_1c804cbfb\">2、封面图源</a></p>","categories":[{"name":"前端","path":"api/categories/前端.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Echarts","path":"api/tags/Echarts.json"}]}